# hilavitkutin-linking

Cross-platform dynamic library loading primitive for the hilavitkutin
extension stack. Pull-based explicit-symbol resolution over dlopen on
Unix and LoadLibrary on Windows. `#![no_std]`, no allocator.

Domain-agnostic: this crate knows how to open a shared library and
resolve a named symbol. It does not know what an extension is. Higher-
level descriptor and lifecycle orchestration lives in
hilavitkutin-extensions.

Renamed from `hilavitkutin-extensions` during design round 202604240615.
